@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
title Aiken contract development workflow

|Design|
start
:read the eUTXO model
(validators are judges,
off-chain is the lawyer);
:model datum / redeemer types;
:express rule as constraints
on the Transaction;

|On-chain|
:aiken new owner/name;
:set plutusVersion = v3
aiken add aiken-lang/stdlib;
:write handler(s)
spend / mint / ...;
:write test + property tests;
repeat
  :aiken check;
repeat while (tests fail\nor ex-units too high?) is (yes) not (no)

|Package|
:aiken build -> plutus.json;
:aiken blueprint apply
(parameters);
:derive address / policy id;

|Off-chain|
:generate types from blueprint;
:build & submit transactions;

|Assurance|
:security pass vs eUTXO
vulnerability catalog;
stop
@enduml
